data.description: Step into luxury as you enter this contemporary three-bedroom, two-bath ranch  in Vermillion, Ohio. The wow factor begins with the grandeur of pillars that greet you at the entrance, setting the tone for the elegance within.  The heart of this home is a chef's dream! Revel in the sleek and modern kitchen featuring eye-catching granite countertops. A perfect blend of style and functionality, this space is sure to inspire culinary delights.  Experience the beauty of nature indoors with recently installed nature stone flooring. This elegant addition enhances the aesthetic appeal while providing durability and easy maintenance. A touch of nature in the heart of your home. Enjoy all the changing seasons from the comfort of your own home in the expansive three seasons room. Flooded with natural light, this versatile space invites you to unwind, entertain, and appreciate the beauty of every season, all year round.  The lower level has been finished creating the perfect space for gatherings and celebrations.  Roof and Gutter Guards 2022 - Sump 2023.  Call today for your private tour!
